review: if you havent gone here go now
i ordered albondigas soup which was just warm and tasted like tomato soup with frozen meatballs
if youre not familiar check it out
couldnt ask for a more satisfying meal
the service was outshining i definitely recommend the halibut
i dont have very many words to say about this place but it does everything pretty well
id say that would be the hardest decision honestly all of ms dishes taste how they are supposed to taste amazing
maybe if they werent cold they would have been somewhat edible
i did not expect this to be so good
and it was way to expensive
